---
import LayoutEN from '../../../layouts/LayoutEN.astro';
import Breadcrumb from '../../../components/Breadcrumb.astro';
---

<LayoutEN
  title="Software"
  description="Astrolads builds e-learnings, community platforms, data dashboards and custom tools. Software that fits the people using it and the purpose it serves."
>
  <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify({
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "Service",
    "serviceType": "Software development",
    "provider": {
      "@type": "Organization",
      "name": "Astrolads",
      "@id": "https://astrolads.com/#organization"
    },
    "areaServed": { "@type": "Country", "name": "Netherlands" },
    "description": "Astrolads develops custom software: e-learnings, community platforms, data dashboards and tools that do exactly what's needed.",
    "url": "https://astrolads.com/en/services/software"
  })} />

  <div class="dienst-page">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <Breadcrumb 
        lang="en"
        items={[
          { name: 'Services', url: '/en/services' },
          { name: 'Software' }
        ]} 
      />

      <!-- Header -->
      <div class="dienst-header">
        <div class="header-titel">
          <p class="section-label">Service</p>
          <h1>Software</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="header-img">
          <img src="/images/diensten/software-header.webp" alt="Software development by Astrolads" width="640" height="420" loading="eager" fetchpriority="high" decoding="sync" />
        </div>
        <div class="header-tekst">
          <p class="header-intro">
            Software is more than code. It's the digital environment where people learn, collaborate and retrieve information. At Astrolads we build custom or scale existing solutions to fit your situation. From e-learnings to community platforms and from data dashboards to tools that do exactly what's needed.
          </p>
          <a href="/en/contact" class="btn-orange">Get in touch</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Applications in 2x2 grid -->
      <div class="toepassingen-grid">
        <div class="toepassing-blok">
          <h3>E-learnings</h3>
          <p>Transferring knowledge in a way that sticks. We develop e-learning environments that match the audience and learning goals. Whether it's professionals, citizens, students or employees. Visually strong, pleasant to use and scalable to as many users as needed. From interactive modules to complete learning paths, together we'll look at what works best for what the audience needs to take away.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="toepassing-blok">
          <h3>Community platforms</h3>
          <p>Sometimes a place to come together is the most important means. With a community platform you give people the space to connect, ask questions and share knowledge. We look together at which solution fits, existing platform or custom-built, and ensure it aligns with the context and the people using it. A platform is only valuable when people actually show up.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="toepassing-blok">
          <h3>Data dashboards</h3>
          <p>Numbers are only useful when you understand them. We build dashboards that translate complex information into something you can actually read and use, tailored to who works with it and what questions need answering. No tangle of graphs, but insights that help make the right decisions.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="toepassing-blok">
          <h3>Custom tools</h3>
          <p>Sometimes the right tool doesn't exist yet. We think along about what's needed and build it, from an internal work process to an accessible application for a broad audience. Practical, considered and made to actually use. No unnecessary features, just exactly what makes the work lighter.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- CTA -->
      <div class="cta-blok">
        <h2>Curious about the software possibilities within your organisation?</h2>
        <p>Whether it's a first sketch or a developed concept, we're happy to think along about what best fits your goal and audience.</p>
        <a href="/en/contact" class="btn-orange">Get in touch</a>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</LayoutEN>

<style>
  .dienst-page { padding: 64px 0 96px; }

  /* Header */
  .dienst-header {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    grid-template-areas:
      "titel slider"
      "tekst slider";
    gap: 0 64px; align-items: start;
    margin-bottom: 96px;
  }
  .header-titel { grid-area: titel; align-self: end; padding-bottom: 16px; }
  .header-img { grid-area: slider; align-self: center; }
  .header-tekst { grid-area: tekst; }
  .header-titel h1 {
    font-size: clamp(36px, 4vw, 52px);
    font-weight: 700; line-height: 1.1; margin-bottom: 0;
  }
  .header-intro { color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.7; font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 28px; }
  .header-img img { width: 100%; border-radius: var(--radius); object-fit: cover; height: 400px; }

  /* Applications 2x2 grid */
  .toepassingen-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 24px;
    margin-bottom: 64px;
  }
  .toepassing-blok {
    background: var(--white);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    padding: 40px;
  }
  .toepassing-blok h3 {
    font-size: 24px;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .toepassing-blok p {
    color: var(--muted);
    line-height: 1.8;
    font-size: 15px;
  }

  /* CTA */
  .cta-blok {
    background: var(--navy);
    color: #fff;
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    padding: 56px 48px;
    text-align: center;
    margin-top: 64px;
  }
  .cta-blok h2 {
    font-size: clamp(24px, 2.5vw, 32px);
    font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .cta-blok p {
    opacity: .8;
    max-width: 520px; margin: 0 auto 28px;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .dienst-page { padding: 32px 0 56px; }

    /* Header: title → photo → text → button */
    .dienst-header {
      display: flex !important;
      flex-direction: column !important;
      grid-template-areas: none !important;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr !important;
      gap: 20px;
      margin-bottom: 56px;
    }
    .header-titel,
    .header-img,
    .header-tekst {
      grid-area: auto !important;
      align-self: auto !important;
      width: 100%;
    }
    .header-titel { order: 1 !important; padding-bottom: 0; }
    .header-img { order: 2 !important; }
    .header-tekst { order: 3 !important; }
    .header-titel h1 {
      font-size: clamp(28px, 7vw, 36px);
      line-height: 1.2;
      margin-bottom: 0;
    }
    .header-intro {
      font-size: 14px;
      line-height: 1.7;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .header-img img {
      aspect-ratio: 16 / 9;
      height: auto !important;
      max-height: 240px;
      width: 100%;
    }

    /* Applications on mobile: 1 column */
    .toepassingen-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 12px;
      margin-bottom: 48px;
    }
    .toepassing-blok {
      padding: 24px;
    }
    .toepassing-blok h3 {
      font-size: 20px;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }
    .toepassing-blok p {
      font-size: 14px;
      line-height: 1.7;
    }

    /* CTA compact */
    .cta-blok {
      padding: 36px 24px;
      margin-top: 48px;
    }
    .cta-blok h2 {
      font-size: 22px;
      line-height: 1.3;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }
    .cta-blok p {
      font-size: 14px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
  }
</style>